      <div class="subfield"><strong>$2 - Source of schema used</strong> <div class="description">MARC code that identifies the source of the schema used to construct the preferred
                              format or the citation for the item described by the bibliographic record.
         </div>
		 
		 <div class="description2 description">
      Code from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/citation.html">Citation Scheme Source Codes</a></em>.
    </div>
		 
